data.description: 3-bedroom, 2.5-bath END UNIT townhouse located in the Huntington Pointe neighborhood. This like new property was built in 2021 and features LVP throughout the first floor, kitchen island allowing for seating, eat in kitchen area, stainless steel appliances, and lots of cabinet storage space. The primary suite offers a walk-in closet, dual sinks and stand-alone shower. The attached 1-car garage offers space for storage, toys or your vehicle. Located near Newport News Golf Club, Newport News Airport, Fort Eustis, entertainment shopping and so much more!
